data.name: fileBrowser.ToolTip
data.value: Data input file must have the following characteristics: 1) Program will always skip the first line in the file. 2) First column holds process name. 3) Second column holds process arrival time. 4) Third column holds process burst time. 5) Forth column holds process priority 6) Each column separated by 1 tab only. Example: Process Arrival Burst Priority P1 0 5 2 P2 1 3 0 . . .
